---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="The Junk Drawer of Useful Tools" 
	description="The Heuheu: A collection of fast, private, and browser-based tools for photos, documents, and data formatting."
>
	<div class="py-16 text-center">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 sm:text-6xl tracking-tight">
			The Junk Drawer of <span class="text-indigo-600">Useful Things</span>
		</h1>
		<p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
			The Heuheu is a helpful desk gremlin that collects the tools you actually need. No accounts, no tracking, and no wait times: everything runs directly in your browser.
		</p>
	</div>

	<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20">
		
		<a href="/tools/webp-converter" class="group p-8 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:border-indigo-300 transition-all border-b-4 border-b-indigo-500">
			<div class="text-indigo-600 mb-4 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest">Image Utility</div>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-indigo-600">WebP Alchemist</h3>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Convert JPG and PNG to WebP instantly. Optimize your site performance without compromising visual quality.</p>
		</a>

		<a href="/tools/unit-converter" class="group p-8 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:border-green-300 transition-all border-b-4 border-b-green-500">
			<div class="text-green-600 mb-4 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest">Mathematics</div>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-green-600">Universal Alchemist</h3>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Fast conversions for length, weight, and temperature. Precise calculations delivered through your own browser engine.</p>
		</a>

		<a href="/tools/json-formatter" class="group p-8 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg hover:border-amber-300 transition-all border-b-4 border-b-amber-500">
			<div class="text-amber-600 mb-4 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest">Developer Tool</div>
			<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 group-hover:text-amber-600">JSON Alchemist</h3>
			<p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Beautify and validate messy JSON strings. Keeps your data private by formatting everything locally.</p>
		</a>

	</div>

